# Spark Stack Monitor — copy ONE of the templates below to `.env` (gitignored).
# The API loads repo-root `.env` on `npm run dev` / `npm start`.
#
#   Head  (192.168.100.11):  cp .env.example.head .env
#   Worker (192.168.100.12): cp .env.example.worker .env
#
# Optional global settings (any `.env`):
#   MONITOR_API_PORT=8787
#   MONITOR_REPO_ROOT=
#   MONITOR_PROVIDER=sglang
#
# Variable reference: see comments inside `.env.example.head` / `.env.example.worker`.
